            <!-- ABOUT / WHO WE ARE -->
            <h2>Welcome to Cathcart United Free Church</h2>

            <p>We are a small fellowship in Cathcart — a group of ordinary people who come together to
                share faith and hope in Jesus. With the help of God's Spirit, we seek to share the Good News
                of Jesus Christ through worship, prayer, caring and teaching within our church family and through
                outreach into our community and beyond.</p>

            <p>We are always delighted to welcome other folk — whether it be online or in-person, visiting
                or staying for a while. <a href="/contact">Drop us a message</a> if you would like to
                find out more or just want to have a wee chat!</p>

